
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <title>Rally8 - Activity based meet-ups.</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <!-- stylesheets -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/compiled/theme.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/vendor/animate.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/vendor/font-awesome.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/custom.css">

    <!-- javascript -->
    <script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.10.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/bootstrap/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/theme.js"></script>

    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
</head>
<body id="home">
{% include 'header.twig' %}
<div id="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="hero-text animated fadeInDown">Meet People. Accomplish Goals.</h1>
        <p class="sub-text animated fadeInDown">
            Pair up with others in your area to achieve your goals together and make new friends.
        </p>
        <div class="cta animated fadeInDown">
            {% if auth %}
                <a href="/dashboard" class="button">Go to my dashboard</a>
            {% else %}
                <a href="/signup" class="button">Sign up free</a>
            {% endif %}

        </div>
        <div class="browsers">
            <img src="/images/ss.png" class="img-responsive" alt="screenshot" style="width:65%;border-radius: 8px" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="features">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row header">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h2>New to town, or want to make new friends?</h2>
                <p>Rally8 is a local solution for you to find new relationships for any activity!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row feature">
            <div class="col-md-6 info">
                <h4>Rally8 is not just for running or dating...</h4>
                <p>
                    Rally8 covers everything from new friendships, gym buddies, video game pals and much more!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 image">
                <img src="/images/inbox.png" class="img-responsive" alt="feature1" style="border-radius: 8px" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="row feature backwards">
            <div class="col-md-6 info">
                <h4>We've made it easy, set up your profile, give your interests and look for some buddies.</h4>
                <p>
                    Rally8 is prefilled with the most popular interests, if you do not see yours; add it!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 image">
                <img src="/images/feature2.png" class="img-responsive" alt="feature2" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row header">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h3>Free for Everyone.</h3>
                <p>Out of a hackathon, this is a quick and free solution. For Hopefully, a common problem</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="slider">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row header">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h3>Includes all pages that a complete theme should have</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 slide-wrapper">
                <div class="slideshow">
                    <div class="btn-nav prev"></div>
                    <div class="btn-nav next"></div>
                    <div class="slide active">
                        <img src="images/slider/slide3.png" alt="slide3" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide">
                        <img src="images/slider/slide4.png" alt="slide4" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide">
                        <img src="images/slider/slide1.png" alt="slide1" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide">
                        <img src="images/slider/slide5.png" alt="slide5" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide">
                        <img src="images/slider/slide2.png" alt="slide2" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<div id="cta">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="form-wrapper">
                    <h4>Ready to start? Create your free account now</h4>
                    <div class="cta">
                        <a href="/signup" class="button">Sign up free</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="bottom-spacer"></div>

{% include 'footer.twig' %}
</body>
</html>